            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer to make it impossible for someone to enter into someone else's house. The word 'ʾAlʾazina' in the incipit may be 
                    seen as a name of demon, which is possibly derived from <foreign xml:lang="ar">al-ʿaziz</foreign> "the Almighty" - one of the
                    eight most powerful names for God in Islam.</p>
            </abstract>
